SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 481
A bill to amend 2016 PA 62, entitled
"Human trafficking notification act,"
by amending sections 2, 3, and 5 (MCL 752.1032, 752.1033, and
752.1035).
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 2. As used in this act:
2 (a) "Adult entertainment establishment" means either of the
3 following:
4 (i) An adult entertainment establishment that holds a topless
5 activity permit under section 916(3) of the Michigan liquor control
6 code of 1998, 1998 PA 58, MCL 436.1916.
7 (ii) Any other retail establishment that provides adult-
8 oriented entertainment in which performers disrobe or perform in an
