1 and simplified Chinese, Bangla, French, Hmong, Vietnamese, and
2 Wolof languages and in any other language determined appropriate by
3 the department in consultation with the attorney general. The
4 department may require the posting of other languages under this
5 subdivision in specified areas of this state due to the languages
6 used within those specified areas, including the language used by
7 any of the following, as applicable:
8 (i) A population with limited English proficiency that, based
9 on reliable data, constitutes 3% or more of the overall population
10 within the geographic area of an entity required to post a human
11 trafficking notice under sections 3 and 4.
12 (ii) Five hundred or more individuals residing within the
13 geographic area of an entity required to post a human trafficking
14 notice under sections 3 and 4.
